 Charli XCX 对 Bowen Yang 在《SNL》中的“Brat”角色扮演“印象深刻” https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-was-very-impressed-with-bowen-yangs-brat-cosplay-on-snl-3799344?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=charli-xcx-对《周六夜现场》中的鲍文杨小子角色扮演非常印象深刻Liberty DunworthThu, 03 Oct 2024 12:39:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsDanceElectronicPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3799344 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杨博文和 Charli XCX" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我有预感它即将到来”</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-was-very-impressed-with-bowen-yangs-brat-cosplay-on-snl-3799344">Charli XCX 对 Bowen Yang 在《SNL》中的“Brat”角色扮演“印象深刻”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杨博文和 Charli XCX" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bowen-Yang-Charli-XCX@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>透露，她最近在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><em>《周六夜现场》</em></a>中的表现给她留下了“非常深刻的印象”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">这是 Charli XCX 的世界，我们只是生活在其中：到目前为止“Brat”夏天的时间表</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手在最近一集热门美国小品节目中写了一个关于她的短剧，其中演员杨博文扮演她，进行了一场受“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">小子</a>”启发的表演。</p><p>在周末播出的这一集里，杨变身为“360”歌手主持“Talk Talk”节目。为了符合热门专辑的美感，布景中充满了亮绿色的道具，演员用英国口音与莎拉·谢尔曼饰演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/troye-sivan">特洛伊·希文</a>交谈。</p><p>现在，查理已经公开谈论了这个短剧，并透露她对杨在这一集中的印象“印象深刻”。</p><p>她在霍华德·斯特恩的<em>SiriusXM</em>频道（通过<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/charli-xcx-reaction-snl-brat-skit-1235121841/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石</em></a>》）发表讲话时说：“我爱鲍文，老实说我认为他做得很好。事实上，我对头发的质地印象非常深刻。我认为这是一顶非常好的假发。这很好，很酷。”</p><p>她继续说：“我认为<em>《周六夜现场》</em>是标志性的，”查理说。 “特洛伊和我，我们预感到它即将到来，所以我们对此感到非常兴奋。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Charli xcx 脱口秀 - SNL" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fTXMjrRZago?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这并不是查理第一次参与<em>《周六夜现场》</em> 。十年前，她在该节目中首次亮相，当时她于 2014 年 12 月作为音乐嘉宾出现，并现场表演了“Boom Clap”和“Break The Rules”。</p><p>她后来于 2022 年重返该剧，当时她参加了当年 3 月的一集现场直播，演唱了《Beg For You》和《Baby》。</p><p>上周末的这一集标志着<em>《周六夜现场》</em>的第 50 季，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jelly-roll">Jelly Roll</a> 。本季的其他音乐嘉宾包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">史蒂维·尼克斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-Roan">查普尔·罗恩</a>。</p><p>至于 Charli 的其他消息，这位歌手正准备发行她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-brat-and-its-completely-different-but-also-still-brat-3793229">的混音版</a>《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Brat</a> 》，并且已经发现了一些神秘的海报，暗示了它可能的潜在合作。 </p><figure id="attachment_3793482" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793482" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3793482" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793482" class="wp-caption-text"> Charli XCX 出席 2024 年 H&amp;M&amp;LONDON 活动。（摄影：Mike Marsland/WireImage/Getty）</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/it-looks-like-the-1975-will-also-feature-on-charli-xcxs-brat-remix-album-3798991">The 1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-teases-bon-iver-and-tinashe-brat-remixes-with-new-billboards-3798689">Bon Iver、Tinashe</a> 、Chappell Roan 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-limp-bizkits-fred-durst-appear-on-charli-xcxs-brat-remix-album-3799309">Limp Bizkit 的 Fred Durst 的</a>标志已被发现， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-caroline-polachek-sophie-and-grimes-to-reportedly-feature-on-charli-xcxs-brat-and-its-completely-different-but-also-still-brat-3794978">网上流传的</a>其他名字包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">Madonna</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caroline-polachek">Caroline Polachek</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sophie">SOPHIE</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grimes">Grimes</a> 。</p><p>根据“Brat”混音版的 Spotify 页面，这张 LP 似乎包含 16 首歌曲，其中 5 首是之前发布的原始曲目列表中歌曲的混音版。到目前为止，新版本已经预告了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/addison-rae">艾迪生·雷 (Addison Rae</a> ) 主演的《Von Dutch》、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">洛德 (Lorde</a> ) 主演的《Girl, So Confusing》、罗宾和容·利恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robyn">(Robyn</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yung-lean">Yung Lean</a> ) 主演的《360》、比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 主演的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">Guess</a> 》、特洛伊·希文 (Troye Sivan) 主演的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-confirms-talk-talk-remix-with-troye-sivan-and-dua-lipa-3792781">Talk Talk</a> 》以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>的口头发言。</p><p>它定于 10 月 11 日发布，可以<a href="https://charlixcx.lnk.to/bratcompletelydifferent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预先保存。</a></p><p>与此同时，Charli XCX 和 Sivan 目前正在进行他们的“Sweat”巡回演唱会的美国站， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/charli-xcx-troye-sivan-sweat-tour-live-review-3796616"><em>NME</em>在五星级评论中表示，“以前的流行乐失败者巩固了他们作为竞技场杀手偶像的地位”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-was-very-impressed-with-bowen-yangs-brat-cosplay-on-snl-3799344">Charli XCX 对 Bowen Yang 在《SNL》中的“Brat”角色扮演“印象深刻”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
