etal_moment） <a href="https://twitter.com/numetal_moment/status/1840924175114056147?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年10月1日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">刚刚在伊利诺伊州贝贝<a href="https://t.co/nBvnJrLAVE">pic.twitter.com/nbvnjrlave</a>的高速公路上看到</p><p> -  3月<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2702.png" alt="✂" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@gooeymaggu） <a href="https://twitter.com/gooeymaggu/status/1841205913732203002?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年10月1日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="reddit-embed-bq" style="height:500px" ><p> <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/charlixcx/comments/1fu5n4j/there_is_a_brat_green_billboard_that_says_fred/">有一个“小子绿色”广告牌，上面写着我附近的弗雷德·杜斯特（Fred Durst）。这很重要吗？</a><br />由<a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/Kodicave/">u/kodicave</a>在<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/charlixcx/">charlixcx</a>中</p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://embed.reddit.com/widgets.js" charset="UTF-8"></script></p><p>尽管尚未确认上述艺术家（包括Durst）是否会出现在专辑中，但期望Charli和Nu-Metal Icon之间的合作并不是太牵强了。</p><p>去年，杜斯特（Durst） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wargasm-team-up-with-limp-bizkits-fred-durst-on-bang-ya-head-3495352">与电子金属二人组合战争杂志（Electal-Metal Duo Wargasm）合作，为“ Bang Ya Head”进行了曲目</a>，然后仅今年就看到他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fred-durst-joins-king-of-trolls-corey-feldman-on-stage-to-confirm-viral-guitar-solo-is-real-hes-fucking-doing-it-3784075">Corey Feldman</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-limp-bizkit-and-jelly-roll-cover-the-who-at-welcome-to-rockville-3755517">Jelly Roll</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-ed-sheeran-sing-behind-blue-eyes-with-limp-bizkit-at-pinkpop-3768202">Ed Sheeran</a>等人在舞台上露面。他还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/limp-bizkit-fred-durst-hardy-soul4sale-3776264">与乡村摇滚歌手Hardy合作，今年夏天早些时候在后者的“ Soul4sale”上</a>。</p><p>在此之前不久， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diiv-team-up-with-fred-durst-for-fake-snl-performance-in-brown-paper-bag-video-3593182">Diiv与Durst的视频分享了他们的单曲“ Brown Paper Bag”</a> ，据报道，他将加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">Billy Corgan</a> ，成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgan-and-fred-durst-to-host-new-shows-on-bill-mahers-podcast-network-3610794">Bill Maher的播客网络上的新节目主持人。</a></p><p>基于“小子”混音的Spotify<a href="https://charlixcx.lnk.to/bratcompletelydifferent">预保存页面</a>，看起来LP包含16首歌曲 - 其中5首以前发布了原始曲目列表中的歌曲的混音。到目前为止，新版本已经以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/addison-rae">艾迪生·雷（Addison Rae</a> ）的“ von荷兰语”为特色，“女孩，如此混乱”与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">洛德</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robyn">（Robyn）</a>和杨·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yung-lean">莱恩（Yung Lean</a> ），“ 360”，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）</a> ，“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">猜猜</a>”，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/troye-sivan">特洛伊·西万（Troye Sivan）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-confirms-talk-talk-remix-with-troye-sivan-and-dua-lipa-3792781">交谈</a>。 ，加上<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>的口头贡献。</p><p>它定于10月11日发布，可以<a href="https://charlixcx.lnk.to/bratcompletelydifferent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预先保存。</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3775063" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3775063" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3775063" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Charli-xcx-live@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Charli-xcx-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Charli-xcx-li